    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what u mean about the chaos part. but when u say the goal of protecting civilians was \"achieved\" but the rest was a \"disaster\"... doesn't that imply the whole thing was basically a mistake? like, if you cause a massive power vacuum and regional instability, does the initial humanitarian success actually count as a success for the intervention as a whole?",
